         </tr>
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td colspan="2"><strong>Subfield Codes</strong><br></td>
         </tr>
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td colspan="1">$a - Current publication frequency (NR) <br>$b - Date of current publication frequency (NR) <br></td>
            <td colspan="1">$6 - Linkage (NR) <br>$8 - Field link and sequence number (R) <br></td>
         </tr>
   </table>
      <hr>
      <h3>FIELD DEFINITION AND SCOPE</h3>
      <p>Current stated publication frequency of either an item or an update to an item. Dates
         are included when the beginning date of the current frequency is not the same as the
                     beginning date of publication.
      </p>
      <p>In records having field 008 (Fixed-Length Data Elements) or field 006 (Fixed-Length Data
         Elements-Additional Material Characteristics) configured for seriality, field 362
         information is related to coded information contained in 008/18 (006/01) (Frequency) and
                     008/19 (006/02) (Regularity). The date(s) of the current publication frequency is given
                     when the beginning date of the current publication frequency is not the same as the
                     beginning date of the publication.
      </p>
      <p>When an item has ceased publication, the current frequency date is closed but remains in
                     field 310.      </p>
      <hr>
      <h3>GUIDELINES FOR APPLYING CONTENT DESIGNATORS</h3>
      <h4><span class="box">&#9632;</span> INDICATORS
      </h4>
      <ul>
         <li>Both indicator positions are undefined; each contains a blank (#).</li>
      </ul>
      <h4><span class="box">&#9632;</span> SUBFIELD CODES
      </h4>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$a - Current publication frequency</strong> <div class="description">Complete statement, exclusive of dates, of the current publication frequency.</div>
